<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="EN">
    <head>
        <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1.5, minimum-scale=0.75">
        <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.ico">

        <script type='text/javascript' src="bower_components/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>

        <!-- Bootstrap core CSS -->
        <link href="bower_components/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <!-- Playlist Rules -->
        <link href="css/playlist-app.css" rel="stylesheet">

        <!-- HTML5 shim and Respond.js IE8 support of HTML5 elements and media queries -->
        <!--[if lt IE 9]>
          <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/libs/html5shiv/3.7.0/html5shiv.js"></script>
          <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/libs/respond.js/1.3.0/respond.min.js"></script>
        <![endif]-->


        <title>DJ Playlist Tools: TrakOffLive</title>
    </head>
    <body>

        <!-- Static navbar -->
        <div class="navbar navbar-default navbar-static-top" role="navigation">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="navbar-header">
                    <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".navbar-collapse">
                        <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
                        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                    </button>
                    <a class="navbar-brand" href="./">Trak Off Live<sup>Beta</sup></a>
                </div>
                <div class="navbar-collapse collapse">
                    <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
{% set navigationMain = ['about', 'search', 'playlist'] %}
{% for item in navigationMain %}
                        <li><a href="./{{ item }}/">{{ item|title }}</a></li>
{% endfor %}                        
                    </ul>
                    <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
{% set navigationRight = ['export', 'settings'] %}
{% for item in navigationRight %}
                        <li><a href="./{{ item }}/">{{ item|title }}</a></li>
{% endfor %} 
                    </ul>
                </div><!--/.nav-collapse -->
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="jumbotron" id="homeImg" style="color: #fff;">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 style="color:#ccc;">Yo, <span>I'll solve it.</span></h1>
                <p>Check out the hook while the DJ <em>resolves</em> it.</p>
                <p>Trak Off Live is your DJ playlist creator, allowing you to 
                    prepare the perfect list whenever you're away from the decks.</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;"><a href="search" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" role="button">Get Started</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr>


        <div>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-7">
                        <h2 class="thinheading">Need a playlist? <span class="text-muted"> Create it now.</span> </h2>
                        <p class="lead">
                            Load your songs' relevant tags into the cloud so you can make the perfect playlist wherever you are.
                        </p>
                        <p class="lead">Like when you're chillin' with your crew before the gig.
                            <em class="text-muted small">"Boat Drinks" 1979 Jimmy Buffett</em></p>
                        <p class="lead">Or let partygoers select a track from your vast library without them spilling drinks on your expensive equipment.</p>
                        <p class="lead">Just 3 easy steps.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-5">
                        <img class="img-responsive img-thumbnail" src="images/boat_drinks.jpg" alt="placeholder image">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr>


        <div>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <h2>Search</h2>
                        <img src="images/searchImage.png" alt="searchImage" class="img-responsive img-thumbnail" />
                        <p>Free form search feature lets you look for a title, album, or artist. Advanced tools can help you generate your playlist by key and BPM.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <h2>Sort</h2>
                        <img src="images/sortImage.png" alt="sortImage" class="img-responsive img-thumbnail" />
                        <p>Drag and drop to sort your songs into the perfect mix. You can even swipe to the left or right to remove the song if you change your mind.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <h2>Export</h2>
                        <img src="images/exportImage.png" alt="exportImage" class="img-responsive img-thumbnail" />
                        <p>Save your list and get a copy via email. Leave a comment for any adjustments or minor details.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px;" class="lead">Then let your DJ take over and deliver your perfect mix.</p>
            <p style="text-align: center;"><a href="search" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" role="button">Get Started</a></p>
        </div>

        <hr>

        <div>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row featurette">
                    <div class="col-md-5">
                        <img class="img-responsive img-thumbnail" src="images/drinks.jpg" alt="placeholder image">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-7">
                        <h2 class="thinheading">Let your audience <span class="text-muted">use #hastags.</span></h2>
                        <p class="lead">
                            Every partygoer wants to hear that song <em> right now </em> but they're far from your booth (good) and your don't want them polluting your booth space (better).
                            They can enter the hastag for the event and add songs at their leisure. 
                            Then the DJ can respect / deny the request at her/his leisure. <em>Yay!</em>                            
                        </p>
                        <p class="lead">
                            <span class="small"><span class="text-muted" style="text-decoration: line-through"><em>"Friday" 2011 Rebecca Black</em></span> Sorry, don't have it.
                                <br /><span class="text-muted"><em>"Closing Time" 1998 Semisonic</em></span> Already?!?!</span>
                        </p>
                        <p style="text-align: center;"><a href="export" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" role="button">Claim your #hashtag</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>



            </div>
        </div>        
{% include 'homefooter.html.twig' %}

        <!-- Bootstrap core JavaScript
        ================================================== -->
        <!-- Placed at the end of the document so the pages load faster -->

        <script src="bower_components/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" type='text/javascript'></script>
        <script src="/js/knockout-3.0.0.js" type='text/javascript'></script>
        <script src="bower_components/modernizr/modernizr.js"></script>
        <script src="bower_components/slip/slip.js"></script>
        <!-- script src="../bower_components/store/dist/store2.min.js"></script -->
        <script src="js/store.min.js"></script>
        <script src="js/songSlipLocalStorage.js"></script>
        <script src="js/searchmusica.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>